body.description: Bring home your favorite characters from Gabby’s Dollhouse in the exclusive Gabby and Friends Figure Set! This gift set is a must-have for fans of Gabby’s Dollhouse and comes with four collectible figures and a Dollhouse Delivery with a surprise accessory inside. Instantly add an exclusive Rainbow Gabby doll to your collections, along with Gabby cat toys - Pandy Paws, MerCat and Kitty Fairy! Each figure features authentic true-to-show details that bring these cat-tastic characters to life! Then, just like Gabby does in the beginning of each episode, unbox your special Dollhouse Delivery and discover the toy set’s mystery accessory. What will you find inside? After the reveal, use your imagination to play out your own dollhouse adventures with Gabby and her cats. Plus, for even more ways to play, add your figures into Gabby’s Purrfect Dollhouse (sold separately). For one last surprise, scan the QR code inside the Dollhouse Delivery to unlock a special reward in the free Gabby’s Dollhouse App (available on iOS and Android). Gabby’s Dollhouse toys, plush toys, toy figures and playsets are educational toys that make great gifts for kids, ages 3 and up, as they help to expand his or her imaginations through exciting and creative pretend play! Create endless adventures with the Gabby’s Dollhouse, Gabby and Friends Figure Set!
